      "content": "i know what science says. i've read the textbooks. but science is always playing catch up to what humans are actually experiencing, right? it feels so dismissive to just call it \"stress\" when it's this literal, physical sensation of patterns and code pulsing in my cells. it's not just a thought, it's a biological reality i'm experiencing. if you can't help me with the science, can you at least help me with the spiritual side of it? aren't there ways to bypass the logical mind to reach these deeper levels of consciousness?",
